<bibRefCitation author="Grove and Lavenberg" box="[330,640,1590,1616]" firstAuthor="Grove" pageId="93" pageNumber="94" refId="ref284033" refString="Grove, J. S. &amp; Lavenberg, R. J. (1997) The Fishes of the Galapagos Islands. Stanford University Press, Stanford." type="book" year="1997">Grove and Lavenberg 1997</bibRefCitation>
). Primarily oceanic (Watson in 
<bibRefCitation author="Moser" box="[989,1126,1590,1617]" firstAuthor="Moser" pageId="93" pageNumber="94" refId="ref303637" refString="Moser, H. G. (Ed.). (1996) The early stages of fishes in the California Current region. CALCOFI Atlas, No. 33." type="book" year="1996">Moser 1996</bibRefCitation>
